item.title: Human Fund Card
item.author: dakotah@pena.name (Dakotah)
item.description: A donation has been made in your name to The Human Fund. This is my interpretation of the infamous Human Fund Charity from a Seinfeld episode. Give out this card for Christmas when you are too cheap to buy anyone gifts à la George Costanza.
